	<div class="comment comment-odd" id="comment-106129106">
		<div class="comment-content" id="comment-106129106-content">
			
			<span id="comment-106129106-content"><p>Silverlight runs on Mac as well (<a href="http://www.microsoft.com/silverlight/resources/installationFiles.aspx?v=2.0)," rel="nofollow">http://www.microsoft.com/silverlight/resources/installationFiles.aspx?v=2.0),</a> and Chiron runs on the Mac via Mono (<a href="http://www.mono-project.com/Main_Page)." rel="nofollow">http://www.mono-project.com/Main_Page).</a></p>

<p>As far as Linux support, the Mono team is working on an implementation of Silverlight called "Moonlight" (<a href="http://www.mono-project.com/Main_Page)." rel="nofollow">http://www.mono-project.com/Main_Page).</a> Chiron also runs on Linux via Mono today.</p></span>
