			<span id="comment-106309896-content"><p>In case anybody is wondering how to customize your powershell prompt to look like  John's.<br />
Create a directory WindowsPowerShell in My Documents and put a file profile1.ps in there with the following content:</p>

<p>function prompt<br />
{<br />
    $host.ui.rawui.WindowTitle = $(get-location)<br />
    Write-Host ("+ " + $(get-location)) -foregroundcolor Yellow<br />
    return "Â» "<br />
}</p></span>
