<p>dsl.rb isn't shipped in DynamicSilverlight yet, it's a small ruby script that simply spits a template file structure; you can achieve the same file structure by just using the hello_world sample found in samples/ruby/hello_world as a starting point. I didn't tell John that it wouldn't ship in our package, so it's my fault =P</p>

